@startuml
title Safehome Security Function - State Machine Diagram

[*] --> Checking : Power-on

state "Checking" as Checking
Checking : do / Check Status

state "Ready to Use" as ReadyToUse
state "Activated" as Activated
state "Monitoring" as Monitoring
state "Alarm" as Alarm
state "False Alarm" as FalseAlarm
state "Off" as Off

Checking --> ReadyToUse : OK
Checking --> Alarm : Problem Detected

ReadyToUse : do / Allow Reset, Activate, Turn Off

Activated --> Monitoring : Activation Successful

Monitoring : do / Start Monitoring

Monitoring --> Alarm : Sensor Triggered
Monitoring --> FalseAlarm : False Alarm
Monitoring --> Monitoring : Time Ends

Alarm : do / Send Alerts

FalseAlarm : do / Continue Monitoring

Off : do / Stop and Return to Normal

@enduml
